{"tid":1379854,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"幫手推","createTime":"2019-07-29T01:01:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T09:15:34.000Z","uid":237739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1ab7e3b16803d8194ec5f211b092365ec5a9b678","tid":1379854,"uid":237739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:01:34.000Z","msg":"請大家深夜玩AOC/三國志 夢遊嘅朋友睇一睇<br />\n<br />\n首先是否似曾相識？玩親都唔夠人打？<br />\n例子：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.bilibili.com/video/av10748768.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2Fav10748768.html&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyy0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=97093cea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.bilibili.com/video/av10748768.html</a><br />\n<br />\n基本打機攻略：<br />\n1. 同我咪左部 2003年美帝片最後武士,先好打機<br />\n<br />\n行軍方式<br />\n<br />\n前線 數隊<br />\n1x總指揮 及 1x副指揮（不需高武力將軍，但要智力高，同要被保護） <br />\n1x訊號員<br />\n1x小隊（50兵），被攻時一定不要落單，否則被擊潰<br />\n2x工兵修理建<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.bilibili.com/video/av38297170.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2Fav38297170.html&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyy0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=f6e4a256\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.bilibili.com/video/av38297170.html</a><br />\n<br />\n突襲 數隊<br />\n1x總指揮 及 1x副指揮（不需高武力將軍，但要智力高，同要被保護）<br />\n2x訊號員<br />\n1x小隊（30兵，要精壯快速武力高），被攻時一定不要落單，否則被擊潰<br />\n<br />\n搜索兵 x 10<br />\n搜索地圖敵方<br />\n<br />\n防守 1隊<br />\n大本營<br />\n訊號員<br />\n防守小隊<br />\n負責守城<br />\n做資源及制作兵力所需<br />\n傳送物資<br />\n<br />\n搜索兵負責通知訊號員<br />\n訊號員通知指揮<br />\n切忌落單被追擊"},{"pid":"bfe0a58cded210b356c2e3a88d137e21aeaa3d61","tid":1379854,"uid":235580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:29:52.000Z","msg":"全部手足同我推！ 如何令黑警有所顧忌有所恐懼！ 如何從狗屋內部分解黑警！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378251</a>"},{"pid":"597872a05524337fa502a179aef62eb4128f88c5","tid":1379854,"uid":237739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":